HEADWORD: Crunode
<hw>Cru"node</hw> <pr>(kr?"n?d)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Prob. fr. L.
<ets>crux</ets> a cross + E. <ets>node</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Geom.)</fld>
